geochemistry 中文翻譯
發音：  
中文翻譯手機版n.地球化學。adj.-ical ,-ist n.agricultural geochemistry:    農業地球化學airborne geochemistry:    航空地球化學analytic geochemistry:    分析地球化學analytical geochemistry:    分析地球化學applied geochemistry:    應用地球化學aquatic geochemistry:    水的地球化學bedrock geochemistry:    基巖地球化學biomass geochemistry:    生物地球化學; 生物質地球化學comparative geochemistry:    比較地球化學core geochemistry:    地核地球化學earthquake geochemistry:    地震地球化學element geochemistry:    元素地球化學environmental geochemistry:    環境地球化學exogenic geochemistry:    外生地球化學experimental geochemistry:    實驗地球化學exploration geochemistry:    勘查地球化學; 勘探地球化學gas geochemistry:    氣體地球化學; 天然氣地球化學general geochemistry:    普通地球化學geochemistry cycle:    地質化學循環geochemistry international:    國際地球化學geochemistry of landscape:    景觀地球化學geochemistry of lithoshere:    巖石圈地球化學geochemistry of solids:    固體地球化學well geochemistry:    鉆井地球化學geochemist:    地球化學家geochemicalprovince:    地球化學區
例句與用法Analytical quality control is essential in geochemistry .在地球化學中，分析質量的控制至關重要。Deterministic models rather than stochastic statistical models has been little pursued in exploration geochemistry .在勘查地球化學中，幾乎沒有採用確定性模型，而是採用推測性模型。Crystal chemistry and geochemistry of thallium minerals鉈礦物晶體化學和地球化學Environmental geochemistry of soil in panzhihua city攀枝花市土壤環境地球化學研究Preface 2 - applied geochemistry : past , present and future現在與未來序二Geochemistry behavior of trace elements in bastard coal煤矸石中微量元素的地球化學行為Ree geochemistry of hypergenesis in basalt以海南島北部玄武巖分佈區為例Bulletin of mineralogy , petrology and geochemistry礦物巖石地球化學通報Tectonic geochemistry of the zhaishang gold deposit , gansu甘肅寨上金礦床構造地球化學特征Research progress of environmental geochemistry環境地球化學研究進展更多例句：  1  2  3  4  5用"geochemistry"造句  
英文解釋the chemistry of the earth''s crust
百科解釋Geochemistry is the science that uses the tools and principles of chemistry to explain the mechanisms behind major geological systems such as the Earth's crust and its oceans. The realm of geochemistry extends beyond the Earth, encompassing the entire solar system and has made important contributions to the understanding of a number of processes including mantle convection, the formation of planets and the origins of granite and basalt.詳細百科解釋



